item.title: Bridget Christie (Part One)
item.description:
This week Emily and Ray take a stroll with the wonderful Bridget Christie, comedian, actor and writer.


Bridget has won a huge following through her acclaimed stand-up shows and memorable TV appearances on Taskmaster and Have I Got News for You.
